Dry Cottage Cheese Filling — savoury

For one batch of dough

Ingredients

• 1½ cups dry cottage cheese, pressed very dry
• 1 large egg yolk
• 1 tbsp unsalted butter, melted and fully cooled
• ¾ tsp fine salt
• ¼ tsp white pepper

⸻

Method

Press cottage cheese through a fine sieve or food mill until completely smooth. Add egg yolk, cooled butter, salt, and white pepper. Mix gently until homogeneous. Chill at least 30 minutes before filling.

⸻

Target Texture

Firm, creamy, lightly elastic. Should hold shape without slumping or weeping.

